    {
      "id": "1914750c-f3ba-805a-bdba-fd73a3590f6b",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "The literature supports the use of portfolios and semantic technologies to improve the pedagogical aspects of the electronic tools being used. The paper presents a conceptual model for such a system, including the desing of learning paths based on a learner’s current level. ",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
        "id": "1914750c-f3ba-805a-bdba-fd73a3590f6b",
        "parent": {
          "type": "page_id",
